---redis高级数据结构</title><link>https://blog.yudlk.com/posts/redis/03-advanced-datastructure/</link><pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2020 22:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>qpt</author><guid>https://blog.yudlk.com/posts/redis/03-advanced-datastructure/</guid><description>&lt;p>本文主要介绍Redis高级数据结构，包括Bitmap(位图)、Hyperloglog、GEO以及使用场景。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Redis教程(二)---redis常用命令</title><link>https://blog.yudlk.com/posts/redis/02-common-cmd/</link><pubDate>Sun, 05 Jan 2020 22:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>qpt</author><guid>https://blog.yudlk.com/posts/redis/02-common-cmd/</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>redis常用命令汇总，包括<code>Key</code>、<code>String</code>、<code>Hash</code>、<code>List</code>、<code>Set</code>、<code>ZSet</code>、发布订阅等待。</p>]]></description></item><item><title>Redis教程(一)---通过docker-compose安装redis</title><link>https://blog.yudlk.com/posts/redis/01-install/</link><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2020 22:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>qpt</author><guid>https://blog.yudlk.com/posts/redis/01-install/</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>本文主要记录了如何在 <code>Linux(CentOS 7)</code> 下安装<code>redis</code>，包括源码编译安装和通过<code>docker compose</code>一键安装。</p>]]></description></item></channel></rss>